            <p class="text-15 lh-18 text-light-1 mt-10">SMPIT Baituljannah menerapkan Kurikulum Merdeka yang diintegrasikan dengan nilai-nilai Islam untuk membentuk generasi yang cerdas, berkarakter, dan berakhlak mulia.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row y-gap-30">
          <!-- Mata Pelajaran Wajib -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="courseCard -type-1 bg-white rounded-8 shadow-4 h-100">
              <div class="courseCard__content px-30 py-30">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-20">
                  <div class="bg-blue-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20">
                    <i class="fas fa-book text-white text-20"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="courseCard__title text-20 fw-600">Mata Pelajaran Wajib</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="courseCard__features">
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Pendidikan Agama Islam & Budi Pekerti</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Pendidikan Pancasila & Kewarganegaraan</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Bahasa Indonesia</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Matematika</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Ilmu Pengetahuan Alam (IPA)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Ilmu Pengetahuan Sosial (IPS)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Bahasa Inggris</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Seni Budaya</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Pendidikan Jasmani, Olahraga & Kesehatan</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Prakarya & Kewirausahaan</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Mata Pelajaran Muatan Lokal -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="courseCard -type-1 bg-white rounded-8 shadow-4 h-100">
              <div class="courseCard__content px-30 py-30">
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-20">
                  <div class="bg-green-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20">
                    <i class="fas fa-mosque text-white text-20"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="courseCard__title text-20 fw-600">Muatan Lokal & Keagamaan</h4>
                </div>
                <div class="courseCard__features">
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Bahasa Arab</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Al-Quran & Hadits</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Akidah Akhlak</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Fiqh</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Sejarah Kebudayaan Islam</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Tahfidz Al-Quran</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Teknologi Informasi & Komunikasi</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Bahasa Daerah (Betawi)</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-15">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Bimbingan Konseling</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-check text-green-1 text-12 mr-15"></i>
                    <span class="text-14">Ekstrakurikuler Wajib (Pramuka)</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Struktur Kurikulum per Kelas -->
    <section class="layout-pt-md layout-pb-md bg-light-6">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-center text-center mb-60">
          <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-9">
            <h2 class="text-30 lh-16 fw-700">Struktur Kurikulum per Kelas</h2>
            <p class="text-15 lh-18 text-light-1 mt-10">Pembagian jam pelajaran dan alokasi waktu untuk setiap tingkat kelas</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row y-gap-30">
          <!-- Kelas VII -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="courseCard -type-1 bg-white rounded-8 shadow-4 text-center">
              <div class="courseCard__content px-30 py-40">
                <div class="bg-purple-1 rounded-8 size-80 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-20">
                  <span class="text-white text-24 fw-700">VII</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="courseCard__title text-20 fw-600 mb-20">Kelas 7</h4>
                <div class="text-left">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Total Jam/Minggu:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">42 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Mata Pelajaran Wajib:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">32 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Muatan Lokal:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">8 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-14">Ekstrakurikuler:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">2 JP</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Kelas VIII -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="courseCard -type-1 bg-white rounded-8 shadow-4 text-center">
              <div class="courseCard__content px-30 py-40">
                <div class="bg-orange-1 rounded-8 size-80 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-20">
                  <span class="text-white text-24 fw-700">VIII</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="courseCard__title text-20 fw-600 mb-20">Kelas 8</h4>
                <div class="text-left">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Total Jam/Minggu:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">42 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Mata Pelajaran Wajib:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">32 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Muatan Lokal:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">8 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-14">Ekstrakurikuler:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">2 JP</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Kelas IX -->
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <div class="courseCard -type-1 bg-white rounded-8 shadow-4 text-center">
              <div class="courseCard__content px-30 py-40">
                <div class="bg-red-1 rounded-8 size-80 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-20">
                  <span class="text-white text-24 fw-700">IX</span>
                </div>
                <h4 class="courseCard__title text-20 fw-600 mb-20">Kelas 9</h4>
                <div class="text-left">
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Total Jam/Minggu:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">44 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Mata Pelajaran Wajib:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">34 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between mb-10">
                    <span class="text-14">Muatan Lokal:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">8 JP</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="d-flex justify-between">
                    <span class="text-14">Persiapan UN/AKM:</span>
                    <span class="text-14 fw-500">2 JP</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Keunggulan Kurikulum -->
    <section class="layout-pt-md layout-pb-md">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-center text-center mb-60">
          <div class="col-xl-8 col-lg-9">
            <h2 class="text-30 lh-16 fw-700">Keunggulan Kurikulum SMPIT Baituljannah</h2>
            <p class="text-15 lh-18 text-light-1 mt-10">Pendekatan pembelajaran yang holistik dan inovatif</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="row y-gap-30">
          <!-- Integrasi Nilai Islam -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="featureCard d-flex align-items-start">
              <div class="featureCard__icon bg-green-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20 flex-shrink-0">
                <i class="fas fa-star-and-crescent text-white text-20"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="featureCard__content">
                <h4 class="featureCard__title text-17 fw-600 mb-10">Integrasi Nilai-Nilai Islam</h4>
                <p class="featureCard__text text-14 lh-18 text-light-1">Setiap mata pelajaran diintegrasikan dengan nilai-nilai Islam untuk membentuk karakter Islami yang kuat pada siswa.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pembelajaran Berbasis Teknologi -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="featureCard d-flex align-items-start">
              <div class="featureCard__icon bg-blue-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20 flex-shrink-0">
                <i class="fas fa-laptop text-white text-20"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="featureCard__content">
                <h4 class="featureCard__title text-17 fw-600 mb-10">Pembelajaran Berbasis Teknologi</h4>
                <p class="featureCard__text text-14 lh-18 text-light-1">Menggunakan teknologi modern dalam proses pembelajaran untuk mempersiapkan siswa menghadapi era digital.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pendekatan Saintifik -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="featureCard d-flex align-items-start">
              <div class="featureCard__icon bg-orange-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20 flex-shrink-0">
                <i class="fas fa-microscope text-white text-20"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="featureCard__content">
                <h4 class="featureCard__title text-17 fw-600 mb-10">Pendekatan Saintifik</h4>
                <p class="featureCard__text text-14 lh-18 text-light-1">Menerapkan metode pembelajaran saintifik: mengamati, menanya, mengumpulkan informasi, mengasosiasi, dan mengkomunikasikan.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Pembelajaran Kontekstual -->
          <div class="col-lg-6">
            <div class="featureCard d-flex align-items-start">
              <div class="featureCard__icon bg-purple-1 rounded-8 size-60 d-flex align-items-center justify-center mr-20 flex-shrink-0">
                <i class="fas fa-globe text-white text-20"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="featureCard__content">
                <h4 class="featureCard__title text-17 fw-600 mb-10">Pembelajaran Kontekstual</h4>
